{"tid":1473674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[寵物台撚狗教學]如何善用狗狗對光源嘅過敏反應","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T11:18:48.000Z","uid":57911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b8296490452d3b729001c4f3fe885cf0dbe547be","tid":1473674,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:10:36.000Z","msg":"首先撚過貓都知，貓仔係會追住支筆點光嚟行，好鬼趣緻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近啲狗狗都學識咗依種技能<br />\n見到光源會「收、收」聲咁叫<br />\n跟住仲會衝過嚟跟住啲光走<br />\n<br />\n近排見啲狗義工帶狗散步<br />\n成日俾啲狗咬親撲親搞到傷晒<br />\n以下我會俾啲小貼士<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔一定執著於帶狗散步，同狗仔玩有好多種方式例如電筒<br />\n<br />\n2. 去狗展唔一定需要一大班人圍住啲狗玩，咁樣反而好易嚇親啲狗<br />\n<br />\n3. 每一區都有狗展，唔好太多狗義工聚埋一齊，搞到啲狗發癲咬人同撲人<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔洗執著於著狗義工制服，可能之前有啲仇狗人士混入咗狗義工，你著狗義工制服反而會刺激啲狗咬你/撲你，普通街坊裝就可以<br />\n<br />\n5. 唔受傷、慳體力、又可以幫狗狗運動，先係我哋啲狗義工最有效率嘅撚狗方式<br />\n<br />\n一齊做個精明狗義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03bc337783f60900c9ad3b1b72f75d42e35bdff","tid":1473674,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3ee03baf32a8087284b78be41518f91ec48d08","tid":1473674,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0612a1045d496ffe8605b3a36b11dc463373c67","tid":1473674,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb8e0ab6aad757c4fde0f8681cb38f0b63773c","tid":1473674,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d84f48f3735e1b49d9791d98158d34a2941ef44","tid":1473674,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT